(140, 'home page', 53, 0, '<p align="center"><font size="2"><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong><strong><em><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #ff0066; font-family: Verdana">The College of Science</span></em></strong></strong></font></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font face="verdana,geneva" size="2"> </font></span><font face="verdana,geneva" size="2">The College of Science was found in accordance with Law No. 143 </font></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><font face="verdana,geneva" size="2">Of 1968. Institutions of the College started at the beginning of the academic year 1968 - 1969. Since its foundation and till end of the academic year<span>&nbsp; </span>1975 - 1976, it consisted of four Departments as follows: </font></span></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><font face="verdana,geneva"><font size="2"><em>Department of Mathematics, Physics, Chemistry and Biology</em>.</font></font></span></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><font face="verdana,geneva"><font size="2">A new <em>department of Geology</em> was established in 1976 - 1977.</font></font></span></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><font face="verdana,geneva" size="2">The College of Science has been steadily growing. At the opening of the College in the academic year 1968 - 1969 it had 243 students. The College expanded and the number of the students are increasing year after year , its present student<span>&nbsp; </span>in academic year 2005 - 2006 reached 1272 undergraduate as well as<span>&nbsp; </span>86<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>graduate students, and its faculty ( College) members reached 161. In<span>&nbsp; </span>meantime the College offers M.Sc. in above mentioned departments, and Ph.D. in Chemistry, Biology, Geology and Physics.</font></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><font face="verdana,geneva"><font size="2"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>In 2001, Kurdistan Museum of Natural History was found in the College of Science. This Museum is a cultural, Scientific, Educational, Tourist &amp; vist research place in which represents an important natural heritage in which deserved to be preserved &amp; exhibited to the people inside &amp; outside of Kurdistan Region. This Museum included all collections &amp; science research to be done about<span>&nbsp; </span>the fauna &amp; flora also include fossils at Kurdistan Region.<br /></font></font></span></p><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><font face="verdana,geneva"><font size="2"><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><span><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: #ff0066; font-family: Verdana">I. <em>The College ( Faculty ) of Science include the following Departments</em>:</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left: 54.4pt; text-indent: -0.25in; text-align: justify; tab-stops: list 54.4pt left 131.2pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Symbol"><span>&nbsp;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana">Chemistry<br /></span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana">Mathematics<br /></span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana">Physics<br /></span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana">Geology<br /></span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana">Biology <br /></span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Symbol"><span>&middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana">Ecology</span></span></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: #ff0066; font-family: Verdana">II. <em>The College Council</em></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>All the administrative, financial, Science and student affairs at the College are Conducted by the Dean, his assistants and the College Council which Comprise the following members: </span></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>1- The Dean<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Head of the Council<br />&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>2- The Heads of all the departments<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Members<br />&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>3- One representative of the teaching staff.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Member<br /></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>4- Student''s representative<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Member</span></p></span></span></font></font></span>', 'ltr', 'left'),
(141, 'home page', 54, 0, '<p align="center"><strong><strong><em><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: #993366; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">The College of Arts</span></em></strong></strong></p><p align="center"><img style="width: 552px; height: 263px" src="http://www.salahaddin-ac.com/photos/arts0.jpg" alt="" width="494" height="286" />&nbsp; </p><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: ''Verdana'',''sans-serif''"><strong>The College of Arts was opened in 1968-1969<br /><br /></strong></span></span><em><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black"><em><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: ''Verdana'',''sans-serif''"><strong>The Foundation of the College</strong></span></em></span><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black"><strong> </strong><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>The Faculty of Arts was established on 11-9-1971. The study started at the beginning of the academic year 1971-1972, in the Department of Kurdish Studies, a branch of Kurdish Language and Literature. The first group of<span>&nbsp; </span>24<span>&nbsp; </span>students graduated in 1974-1975.<span>&nbsp; </span>The section of economics was established in the academic year 1972-1973. In the year 1975-1976 the faculty of Arts was divided into the following sections:</span></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: ''Verdana'',''sans-serif''">1- Department of Kurdish Language comprises of:</span></p><p style="margin-left: 39.2pt; text-indent: -0.25in; text-align: justify; tab-stops: list 39.2pt left 131.2pt"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: ''Verdana'',''sans-serif''"><span>a.<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: ''Verdana'',''sans-serif''">Section of Kurdish Language and Literature.</span></p><p style="margin-left: 39.2pt; text-indent: -0.25in; text-align: justify; tab-stops: list 39.2pt left 131.2pt"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: ''Verdana'',''sans-serif''"><span>b.<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: ''Verdana'',''sans-serif''">Section of Sociology.</span></p><p style="margin-left: 39.2pt; text-indent: -0.25in; text-align: justify; tab-stops: list 39.2pt left 131.2pt"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: ''Verdana'',''sans-serif''"><span>c.<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: ''Verdana'',''sans-serif''">Section of Economics.<br /></span></p><p style="margin-left: 13.5pt; text-indent: -13.5pt; text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: ''Verdana'',''sans-serif''">2- Department of Economics and Administration ( which was transferred to the Faculty of Administration from the academic year 1976-1977).</span></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: ''Verdana'',''sans-serif''"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>In the year 1977-1978 the name of Kurdish Studies Department was changed to Kurdish Language Department. Thereby the Faculty of Arts became as follows:</span></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: ''Verdana'',''sans-serif''"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><span>i.<span>&nbsp; </span>Kurdish Language Department:</span></p><p style="margin-left: 1in; text-indent: -0.75in; text-align: justify; tab-stops: .5in list 1.0in left 131.2pt"><span st