b-stops: list 39.2pt left 131.2pt" align="left"><font face="verdana,geneva"><font color="#000000"><font size="2"><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black"><span>a.<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font size="2">&nbsp; </font></span></span></span></font><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black"><font size="2">Section of Kurdish Language and Literature.</font></span></font></font></p><p style="margin-left: 39.2pt; text-indent: -18pt; text-align: justify; tab-stops: list 39.2pt left 131.2pt" align="left"><font face="verdana,geneva"><font color="#000000"><font size="2"><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black"><span>b.<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></font><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black"><font size="2">Section of</font><font size="2"> <font size="2">Sociology</font>.</font></span></font></font></p><p style="margin-left: 39.2pt; text-indent: -18pt; text-align: justify; tab-stops: list 39.2pt left 131.2pt" align="left"><font face="verdana,geneva"><font color="#000000"><font size="2"><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black"><span>c.<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></font><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black"><font size="2">Section of</font><font size="2"> <font size="2">Economics</font>.</font></span></font></font></p><p style="margin-left: 13.5pt; text-indent: -13.5pt; text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt" align="left"><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black"><font face="verdana,geneva" size="2" color="#000000">2- Department of Economics and Administration ( which was transferred to the Faculty of Administration from the academic year 1976-1977).</font></span></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt" align="left"><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black"><font face="verdana,geneva"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>In the year 1977-1978 the name of Kurdish Studies Department was changed to Kurdish Language Department. Thereby the Faculty of Arts became as follows:</font></font></font></span></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt" align="left">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt" align="left"><font face="verdana,geneva" size="2" color="#000000"><span>i.<span>&nbsp; </span>Kurdish Language Department:</span></font></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt" align="left"><font face="verdana,geneva" size="2" color="#000000"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;1. </span></font><font face="verdana,geneva"><font color="#000000"><font size="2"><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black; font-family: Wingdings"><span><span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp; </span></span></span></font><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black"><font size="2">Section of</font><font size="2"> <font size="2">Linguistic<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2.</font></font></span></font></font><font face="verdana,geneva"><font color="#000000"><font size="2"><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black; font-family: Wingdings"><span><span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></font><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black"><font size="2">Section of</font><font size="2"> <font size="2">Literature</font> <font size="2">Studies</font></font></span></font></font></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 36.0pt 131.2pt" align="left"><font face="verdana,geneva" size="2" color="#000000"><span>ii.<span>&nbsp; </span>Arabic Language Department :</span></font></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 36.0pt 131.2pt" align="left"><font face="verdana,geneva" size="2" color="#000000"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1.</span></font><font face="verdana,geneva"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span style="color: black; font-family: Wingdings"><span><span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="color: black"><font face="verdana,geneva">Section of Linguistic Studies<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2.&nbsp;</font></span></font></font></font><font size="2"><font face="verdana,geneva" color="#000000"><span style="color: black">Section of Literature Studies</span></font></font></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 36.0pt 131.2pt" align="left"><font face="verdana,geneva"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span>iii. Section of Sociology.</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></font></font></font></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt" align="left"><font face="verdana,geneva" size="2"><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black"><font color="#000000"><font size="2">In</font> <font size="2">1985</font> <font size="2">Arabic Language, History and English Language Departments were added. Then department of Geography, Islamic studies, Archaeology and finally Evening English department , Persian &amp; French language were added.</font></font></span></font></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt" align="left"><font color="#000000"><span><font face="verdana,geneva"><font size="2"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>The Faculty of Arts aims at providing students with the best quality teaching, and research in arts, the humanities and social sciences. These are field concerned with understanding the ways in which society and culture have developed, how we deal with our own and other cultures, and how we understand and co- ape with social and cultural changes. For undergraduate students, the Faculty provides a broad range of study options within the Bachelor of Arts degree. <br /><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </font></font></span><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''"><font face="verdana,geneva"><font size="2">Studies in the college were confined to under graduate studies until 1968 when<span>&nbsp; </span>M.A. studies were commenced in both Kurdish and Arabic departments, in 1987 the History department was established, afterwards, the Geography, Sociology, English, Archaeology and Islamic studies departments commenced their M.A. Programs. Later, Ph.D. studies by courses started in History, Kurdish, Geography, Arabic and English departments. The academic year 1995-1996 witnessed the graduation of the first Ph.D. student</font></font></span></font></p></span><p style="text-align: center; tab-stops: 131.2pt" align="center">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center; tab-stops: 131.2pt" align="center">&nbsp;</p></span>', 'ltr', 'left'),
(143, 'home page', 56, 0, '<p align="center"><strong><br /><em><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: #993366; font-family: Verdana"><br />College of Administration and Economics</span></em> </strong></p><p><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><span><span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><span><span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font face="verdana,geneva">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </font></span></span></span><span><span style="font-size: 9pt"><font face="verdana,geneva" size="2">The College of Administration And Economics is </font></span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt"><font face="verdana,geneva" size="2">One of the colleges of university of salahaddin in Iraqi federal<span>&nbsp; </span>Kurdistan region- Hawler, about 2 kilometers of center Hawler.</font></span><span style="font-size: 9pt"><font face="verdana,geneva"><font size="2"><br />Its humble beginning date back to the establishment of the Division of Economics within the Department of Kurdish Studies, College of Arts, in the fall&nbsp; 1972 . However, it started as a College under College of Administration with two departments, Administration and Statistics in 1976/1977. The College started with 180 students in&nbsp; 1976/1977&nbsp; with the present enrolment&nbsp; 2557 .</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;</font>&nbsp;</span> <br /></span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><span><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt" align="center"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: red; font-family: Verdana"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><font face="verdana,geneva" size="2">In the academic year 1987/1988<span>&nbsp; </span>the College was renamed<span>&nbsp; </span>College of Administration and Economics following the restitution of the Department of Economics and remained as such till present. In 1988/1989<span>&nbsp; </span>the Department of Accounting was added. Thus, the college has become a full fledged institution with interrelated degree granting departments.</font></span></p></span></span><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><font size="2">Following the enactment of Iraqi Kurdistan Region''s Higher Education and Scientific Research Law in<span>&nbsp; </span>1994, the main goals of the college have become more clearly drawn and fall in line with the objectives set in the said law. These objectives can be summarized as follows: </font></span></p><ul><li><div style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><font size="2">Training young men and women for specialized professions for public and private sectors and preparing them for further career specialists.</font></span></div></li><li><div style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; text-align: justify; tab-stops: list .25in left 131.2pt"><font size="2"><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><span><span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">G</span></span></span><span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana">ranting full study leave for bright graduates to get on to become well qualified staff on the college faculty. </span></span></font></div></li><li><div style="margin-left: 27pt; text-indent: -27pt; text-align: justify; tab-stops: list .25in left 131.2pt"><span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><font size="2">Providing qualified research assistants to work on public and private projects relating to economic development and scientific progress.</font></span></span></div></li><li><div style="margin-left: 27pt; text-indent: -27pt; text-align: justify; tab-stops: list .25in left 131.2pt"><font size="2"><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><span><span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana">Solving economic, social and administrative problems aimed at real issues of the day.</span></span></font></div></li><li><div style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><font size="2">The period of study in this College is four year for a B.Sc. degree.</font> </span></div></li></ul><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><font color="#993366"><strong>I. The College ( Faculty ) of Administration and Economics<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>include the following Departments:</strong></font></span></p><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Symbol"><span><span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Symbol"><span><span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''"><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Symbol"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana">Economics Department<br /></span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Symbol"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana">Administration Department<br /></span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Symbol"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana">Statistics Department<br /></span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Symbol"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &middot;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana">Accounting Department</span></strong></span></span></span></span>&nbsp; <p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><strong><font color="#993366">II. The College Council</font></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><font size="2">All the administrative, financial, Science and student affairs at the College are conducted by the Dean, his assistants and the College Council which Comprise the following members: </font></span></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><font size="2"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>1- The Dean<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Head of the Council&nbsp;<br /></font></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana"><font size="2"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>2- The Heads of all the departments<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Members&nbsp;<br /></font></span><font size="2"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>3- One representative of the teaching staff.<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Member&nbsp;<br /></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>4- Student''s representative<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Member</span></font></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><strong><em><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: #993366; font-family: Verdana">III. The College has the following specialized centers and</span><span style="color: black"> </span></em></strong><strong><em><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: #993366; font-family: Verdana">units:&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></em></strong><span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black; font-family: Georgia"><br /></span></span><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: black; font-family: Wingdings"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black; font-family: Georgia"><font face="verdana,geneva"><font size="1"><font size="2">The Center of Computer<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black; font-family: Georgia"><font size="2"><font face="verdana,geneva">The center of</font> <font face="verdana,geneva">Internet</font></font>&nbsp;</span></font></font></span></span></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: #993366; font-family: Verdana"><em>IV. The College has the number of committee.</em></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: #993366; font-family: Verdana"><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </em></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: #993366; font-family: Verdana"><em><span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana">The Scientific Committee<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></em><em><span><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana">Academic Promotion</span></span></em></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt">&nbsp;</p>', 'ltr', 'left'),
(144, 'home page', 57, 0, '<p align="center"><em><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #993366; font-family: Georgia"><font color="#ff00ff"><strong><font color="#993366">College of</font></strong></font> </span><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #993366; font-family: Georgia">Science</span><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #993366; font-family: Georgia"> Education</span></strong></em></p><p align="center"><img src="http://www.salahaddin-ac.com/photos/ScienceEducation.jpg" border="0" alt="" width="403" height="257" align="middle" />&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">Establishment of Science Education College</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-indent: -9pt; text-align: justify; tab-stops: list .5in"><span style="font-family: ''Arial Unicode MS'',''sans-serif''"><span>&bull;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;<font size="2"> </font></span></span></span><span style="font-family: ''Verdana'',''sans-serif''"><font size="2">It is first college of the kind in Kurdistan. It has been inaugurate in 1976 - 1977, when university''s headquarters was in Sulaimani City, when consisted of two scientific departments:<br /></font></span><span style="font-family: ''Arial Unicode MS'',''sans-serif''"><span><font size="2">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </font></span></span><font size="2"><span style="font-family: ''Verdana'',''sans-serif''">1-Chemistry and Biology.<br /></span><span style="font-family: ''Verdana'',''sans-serif''">&nbsp;&nbsp; 2-Physics and Mathematics.</span></font></p><p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-indent: -9pt; text-align: justify; tab-stops: list .5in"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: ''Arial Unicode MS'',''sans-serif''"><span>&bull;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family: ''Verdana'',''sans-serif''">In 1978 - 1979, the two departments were dived in to four independent departments and the unit of Computer has turned in to a department in 1999 - 2000 because of the significance of computer skills in college student''s career.</span></font></p><p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-indent: -9pt; text-align: justify; tab-stops: list .5in"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: ''Arial Unicode MS'',''sans-serif''"><span>&bull;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family: ''Verdana'',''sans-serif''">The first group of postgraduate students in chemistry and biology department were accepted in 1987 - 1988. </span></font></p><p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-indent: -9pt; text-align: justify; tab-stops: list .5in"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: ''Arial Unicode MS'',''sans-serif''"><span>&bull;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: ''Verdana'',''sans-serif''">Nowadays, Science Education College comprises five departments: Chemistry, Biology, Physics, Mathematics and Computer.</span></font></p><p style="margin-left: 9pt; text-indent: -9pt; text-align: justify; tab-stops: list .5in"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: ''Arial Unicode MS'',''sans-serif''"><span>&bull;&nbsp;<span style="font: 7pt ''Times New Roman''"> </span></span></span><span style="font-family: ''Verdana'',''sans-serif''">It is worth</span><span style="font-family: ''Verdana'',''sans-serif''">y to</span><span style="font-family: ''Verdana'',''sans-serif''"> mention that College of Physical Education and College of Education for Humanity Science were parts of our college before being separate and becoming two independent Colleges.</span></font></p>', 'ltr', 'left'),
(145, 'home page', 58, 0, '<strong><strong><em><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #993366; font-family: Georgia"><strong><em><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #993366; font-family: Georgia"><p align="center"><br />&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center; tab-stops: 131.2pt" align="center"><strong><em><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #993366; font-family: Georgia">College</span></em></strong><strong><em><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #993366; font-family: Georgia"> of </span></em></strong><strong><em><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #993366; font-family: Georgia">Humanities</span></em></strong><strong><em><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #993366; font-family: Georgia"> Education </span></em></strong></p><p style="text-align: center; tab-stops: 131.2pt" align="center"><strong><em></em></strong></p></span></em></strong></span></em></strong></strong><div style="text-align: center"><img src="http://www.salahaddin-ac.com/photos/Humanities%20Education.JPG" alt="Humanities Education" width="465" height="229" /></div><p align="center"><span>The College of Education for Human Science was opened in 1976-1977</span>&nbsp; </p><p style="text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt" align="left">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt" align="left">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt" align="left"><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <font size="2">The College was established at the beginning of the academic year 1976/1977.</font><span><font size="2">&nbsp; <br /></font></span></span><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black"><font size="2">The <strong><em>main purpose</em></strong> of the College is to graduate qualified teachers for secondary schools.<span>&nbsp; </span>Education and Psychology is supervised by the dean directly, since it is not a department yet. </font></span></p><p style="text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt" align="left"><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black"><font size="2">&nbsp;&nbsp; Arabic<span>&nbsp; </span>and Psychology departments were inaugurated in 1985/1986.<span> </span>In 1991,<span>&nbsp; </span>after<span>&nbsp; </span>the uprising and the great Kurdish exodus, Kurdish Language department has been announced as a re enforcements of Kurdish identity and entity in 1992/1993.<span>&nbsp; </span></font></span></p><p style="text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt" align="left"><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black"><font size="2">The graduate of English language from college Arts were not sufficient to compensate the lacks of English teachers in schools, in the academic year<span>&nbsp; </span>1998/1999<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>the English language Department was added. In academic year 2004/2005 the geography Department was added to the College.</font></span></p><p style="text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt" align="left">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt" align="left">&nbsp;</p>', 'ltr', 'left'),
