(148, 'home page', 61, 0, '<p align="center"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#ff00ff"><em><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: #993366"><font color="#ff00ff"><strong><em><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: #ffcc66">College</span></em><em><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: #ffcc66"> of </span></em><em><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: #ffcc66">Agriculture</span></em></strong></font></span></em></font></font>&nbsp; </p><p align="center">&nbsp;</p><div align="center" style="text-align: center"><strong><img style="width: 373px; height: 197px" src="http://www.salahaddin-ac.com/photos/Agriculture.JPG" border="0" alt="Agriculture college" width="419" height="250" /><br /></strong></div><div style="text-align: center"><span style="font-size: 11pt"><span><p>&nbsp;</p><span style="color: black"><p style="text-justify: kashida; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><strong>&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 11pt"><span><span style="color: black"><strong><font size="4">The foundation of the College</font></strong></span></span></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-justify: kashida; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><em><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></em><font face="verdana,geneva" size="2">The college was established in 1968, but unfortunately it was closed in 1987 due to political reasons. The necessity to provide the region with trained agricultural cadres and teaching staff promoted the </font></span><font face="verdana,geneva"><font size="2"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">Kurdistan</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''"> regional government to reopen the college. Actually it was opened in 1996.</span></font></font></p><p style="text-justify: kashida; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font face="verdana,geneva"><font size="2"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Around nine hundred and ten students are currently following programs leading to B.SC, M.Sc. and Ph.D. in different disciplines of agriculture.</font></font></span></p><p style="text-justify: kashida; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%"><font face="verdana,geneva"><font size="2"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><span>&nbsp; </span>An experimental station having an area of 87 hectares at Grdarasha site, about 4 km to the south of </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">Erbil</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''"> is linked to the collage for practical training and performing research works.</span></font></font></p><p style="text-justify: kashida; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font face="verdana,geneva"><font size="2"><span>&nbsp; </span>It is worthwhile to mention that the college along with the other colleges of the university has been facing many shortages. Most of them were related with the double embargo, to with the region was subjected, therefore, the progress was slowly been made in restoring its former status in the international academic community.</font></font></span></p><p style="text-justify: kashida; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font face="verdana,geneva"><font size="2"><span>&nbsp; </span>An enormous task faces the university at present, the task of taking playing an important role in restructuring the country. One of our aspirations is to establish a new campus for our college outside the city with furnished lecture halls and equipped laboratories to raise educational standard and enhancing student''s scientific abilities.</font></font></span></p><p style="text-justify: kashida; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%"><font face="verdana,geneva"><font size="2"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><span>&nbsp; </span>Another aspect that makes proper agriculture training indispensable for the region is establishing a modern experimental farm affiliated to the college to promote research activities and demonstrate research methodologies to the students the final aim is to rebuild the </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''">Kurdistan</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''"> rural community. </span></font></font></p><p style="text-justify: kashida; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font face="verdana,geneva"><font size="2"><span>&nbsp; </span>Attention also given<span>&nbsp; </span>to create a scientific link between our college and other academic institutions all over the world via mutual exchange of teaching staffs, arrangement of training courses, obtaining sabbatical leaves and so forth .</font></font></span></p><p style="text-justify: kashida; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font face="verdana,geneva"><font size="2"><span>&nbsp; </span>Furthermore, efforts will be spent to set up an internet center to enable the students and teaching staff have access to the updated and recent knowledge and development.</font></font></span></p><p style="text-justify: kashida; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font face="verdana,geneva" size="2">&nbsp; Since our library needs the on-line information on the ongoing research in the academic world, attempts will also be made to make a steady inflow of new references and periodicals to update the predominantly out -dated library stock.</font></span></p><p style="text-justify: kashida; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font face="verdana,geneva" size="2">&nbsp; We attaches great importance to the postgraduate programs through creating scientific atmosphere to raise new generations of teaching staffs to respond to the challenges of future problems. In addition, our concern''s to cooperate all together to restore the high stature of the university teacher in a near future.</font></span></p><p style="text-justify: kashida; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font face="Verdana" size="2"><br />see <a href="http://www.salahaddin-ac.com/photos/seemore.pdf"><font color="#3366ff">more</font></a></font></span></p><p style="text-align: center; tab-stops: 131.2pt" align="left">&nbsp;</p></span><p style="text-justify: inter-ideograph; margin-left: 54.4pt; text-indent: -18pt; text-align: justify; tab-stops: list 54.4pt left 131.2pt">&nbsp;</p></span></span></div>', 'ltr', 'left'),
(149, 'home page', 62, 0, '<p align="center"><strong><strong></strong></strong></p><p align="center"><strong><strong><font color="#800000">Welcome&nbsp;to </font><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black"><font color="#800000">Physical Education College</font> </span></strong></strong></strong></p><p><strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong> <div style="text-align: center"><img src="http://www.salahaddin-ac.com/photos/Physical%20Education.JPG" alt="" /></div></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style="text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><strong><em><span style="color: black">The Foundation of the College</span></em></strong></p><p style="text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; tab-stops: 131.2pt"><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: black"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></strong><span style="font-size: 11pt">The </span><span style="font-size: 11pt">college</span><span style="font-size: 11pt"> of </span><span style="font-size: 11pt">physical Education</span><span style="font-size: 11pt"> was a department which belongs to college of education. In 1998 this department become a college of physical education by itself up to now. The Faculty offers the Bachelor''s degree, and the Master''s degree in Physical Education.</span></p><p style="text-justify: kashida; margin: 0.8pt 0cm; text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-justify: kashida; margin: 0.8pt 0cm; text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-justify: kashida; margin: 0.8pt 0cm; text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 10pt">Building &amp; Research Facilities...</span></u></strong></p><p style="text-justify: kashida; margin: 0.8pt 0cm; text-align: justify; text-kashida: 0%"><span style="font-size: 11pt">Besides the main building, the Faculty of Physical Education occupies two major buildings in its current location . In addition to lecture rooms, the buildin